de'', edited by [[Amanda Holden (writer)| Amanda Holden]]. New York: Penguin Putnam. {{ISBN|9780140514759}}. * Wiley, W. L. (1960). ''The Early Public Theatre in France''. Cambridge, Massachusetts: Harvard University Press. {{OCLC|331219}}. Greenwood Press reprint (1973): {{ISBN|9780837164496}}.
